---
description: "HTML templates must be semantic, accessible, and tiny"
globs: ["templates/**/*.html"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Exactly one `<h1>`; heading levels in order.
- Required landmarks: `header`, `main`, `footer`; include a skip link.
- Use `<figure><img><figcaption>` for content images; no presentational images as content.
- Add JSON-LD slot; never ship a page without required schema fields.
- No inline event handlers; zero client JS on content pages.
